s=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@supports</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">font-variation-settings</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"wdth\"</span> 900<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ...<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"zajimave-zdroje-a-nastroje\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#zajimave-zdroje-a-nastroje\" aria-label=\"zajimave zdroje a nastroje permalink\" class=\"Blog-share before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Zajímavé zdroje a nástroje</h2>\n<h3 id=\"v-fontscom\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#v-fontscom\" aria-label=\"v fontscom permalink\" class=\"Blog-share before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>v-fonts.com</h3>\n<p>Nabízí přehledný zdroj variabilních fontů kde si můžete vyzkoušet jednotlivé variable fonty a pomocí sliderů vytvářet jejich variace.\n<a href=\"https://v-fonts.com/\">https://v-fonts.com/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"axis-praxiscom\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#axis-praxiscom\" aria-label=\"axis praxiscom permalink\" class=\"Blog-share before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>axis-praxis.com</h3>\n<p>Další knihovna variable fontů, které lze editovat přímo na stránce.\n<a href=\"https://www.axis-praxis.org/\">https://www.axis-praxis.org/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"playtypedetailcom\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#playtypedetailcom\" aria-label=\"playtypedetailcom permalink\" class=\"Blog-share before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>play.typedetail.com</h3>\n<p>Interaktivní playground pro variable fonty. Tento nástroj je spíše pro návrháře.\n<a href=\"http://play.typedetail.com/\">http://play.typedetail.com/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"firefox-font-inspector\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firefox-font-inspector\" aria-label=\"firefox font inspector permalink\" class=\"Blog-share before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firefox font inspector</h3>\n<p>Výborným nástrojem pro vývojáře a designéry jsou DevTools pro Firefox. Ty obsahují v tabu Inspector záložku <code class=\"language-text\">Fonts</code>, kde se dají pomocí GUI editovat vlastnosti fontů.\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/4e6ec/firefox-font-inspector.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.42857142857142%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/c54d4/firefox-font-inspector.webp 175w,\n/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/a3432/firefox-font-inspector.webp 350w,\n/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/426ac/firefox-font-inspector.webp 700w,\n/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/97d4f/firefox-font-inspector.webp 827w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/4edbd/firefox-font-inspector.png 175w,\n/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/13ae7/firefox-font-inspector.png 350w,\n/static/10716dcca9384c00ea60bee57a3e18a3/8c557/firefox-font-inspector.png 700